      <title>Even simpler way of calling your AWS backend</title>
      <link>https://magnuswahlstrand.github.io/post/2022-07-09-trpc-with-lambda-function-urls-on-aws/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Jul 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
